            </td>
          </tr>

          <tr>
            <td class="events">
              <h3><a class="anchro" id="top" name="jubilee"></a>Jubilee Running 10K, Sunday 26th June 9.30am</h3>
              <p>Runners and Walkers welcome. A slightly undulating, 10K all terrain course encompassing Selsdon, Sanderstead and Warlingham. Entrants must be 15 years of age or older. For an entry form please contact the Jubilee Church Office on 020 8651 2807 email <%= mail_to "office@croydon-jubilee.co.uk" %></p>
            </td>
            <td class="events">
              <h3><%= link_to image_tag("small-images/jubilee100.jpg", alt: "Jubilee logo"), "resource/jubilee_running.pdf" %></h3>
            </td>
          </tr>




